                                        <p class="mb-0">
                                            kabshak.com may contain links to other websites of interest. If you use any of these links to leave our website, The Kabshak does not have any control over that other website or the information that the other website may collect from you. We have no control over and assume no responsibility for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party sites or services or for the protection and privacy of any information which you provide while visiting such other websites.
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
