                                    <div id="collapse-8" class="card-body expanded" style="display: block;">
                                        <p class="mb-0">
                                            We may be required by law, for example, through potential or actual litigation, court order, public or governmental authorities, or rules and regulations within or outside your country of residence to disclose all or part of your information to third parties. We may also deem it necessary to make such a disclosure in the event of an issue of national security, law enforcement, or other such similar situations as we deem necessary including, for example, allegations of alleged infringement of copyright, trademarks or other third parties’ rights.                                       
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-12 mb-8">
                            <div class="accordion accordion-bg accordion-gutter-md accordion-border">
