                                    <div id="collapse-9" class="card-body expanded" style="display: block;">
                                        <p class="mb-0">
                                            We share your personal information with third-party service providers in order to provide our website functionality and services to you including third parties who assist us with:                                       
                                        </p>
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>Information and data processing</li>
                                            <li>Credit and payment processing</li>
                                            <li>Order fulfillment</li>
                                            <li>Managing and hosting data</li>
                                            <li>Consumer research or satisfaction surveys</li>
                                            <li>To improve our services</li>
                                            <li>To provide service on our behalf</li>
                                            <li>To perform service, maintenance and repair-related activities</li>
                                            <li>To assist us in analyzing how our website and services are used</li>
                                        </ul>
                                        <p>These third party companies may have access to your information to perform the tasks described above. However, they are obligated not to disclose or use your information for any other purpose. We do not provide your information to third parties that enable them to engage in any direct marketing to you without your express consent.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-12 mb-8">
                            <div class="accordion accordion-bg accordion-gutter-md accordion-border">
