                                            If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:info@kabshak.com">info@kabshak.com</a>.
                                            <br />
                                            Updated by Kabshak on Nov 20, 2022                                       
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>
